---
// Terminal & AI-assisted workflow section with real screenshot
---

<section id="terminal" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text content -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-cyan/20 bg-cyan/5 text-cyan text-xs font-medium mb-6">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5" /><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19" />
          </svg>
          Persistent Terminals
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Terminal sessions<br />
          <span class="text-cyan">attached to each worktree.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Every worktree has its own built-in terminal area with multiple tabs. Sessions are backed by a 
          dedicated tmux server, so they survive app restarts and persist across sessions.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CBFE0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Multiple tabs and split panes</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Run multiple terminal sessions per worktree with tab support. Split panes horizontally or vertically within a session. Mix shell tabs with AI-assisted tabs and switch between them.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CBFE0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">LLM profiles</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Define named profiles for AI tools with a command, default profile flag, and color. Launch a plain shell or an LLM session from the same place. Color-coded tabs distinguish AI sessions from regular terminals.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CBFE0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Powered by Ghostty</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Built on Ghostty for a native terminal experience. Rename and recolor sessions after creation. Clear guidance when tmux is unavailable.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Video demo -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan/10 to-purple/5 rounded-2xl blur-xl scale-105"></div>
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-bg-surface shadow-xl">
            <video 
              autoplay 
              loop 
              muted 
              playsinline
              class="w-full h-auto"
              poster="/images/worktree-detail.png"
            >
              <source src="/images/terminal-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              <img 
                src="/images/worktree-detail.png" 
                alt="FlowTree terminal with multiple tabs and split panes" 
                class="w-full h-auto"
              />
            </video>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
